            "id": "fs-id2025294",
            "alt": "The left photo shows a plant that has wilted, with dark green leaves that are shriveled, and appear dry.  The photo on the right shows a healthy plant, with broad light green leaves that appear soft and pliable.",
            "src": "../../media/Figure_05_02_09.jpg",
            "mimeType": "image/jpg"
          }
